Currently GMail groups emails together even if they are from different requests. That makes it hard to follow the updates of each request. 

The reason GMail does that is due to the subject title. In this case the subject is "[HR-JIRA] [People Central Service Desk] Job Change" and it doesn't mention the specific ID of the issue. 

It would be great if the issue id or some other unique identifier could be added to the subject to enable proper threading in Gmail.

